# Stack

- Laravel 12.51.0
- Inertia 
- React 19.2.4 
- TypeScript
- TailwindCSS
- MySQL
- Laravel Sail (Docker)
- PHPUnit


## Requirements

- Docker
- Docker Compose
- Composer


## API Endpoints

GET    /api/articles
GET    /api/articles/{id}
POST   /api/articles
POST   /api/articles/{id}/comments

## Postman Collection
