<img src="newman.png" alt="postman" width="500" height="300">



## Installation

Clone repository:

```bash
git clone https://github.com/Wasuremeno/polis_api_test.git
cd polis_api_test
./vendor/bin/sail up
./vendor/bin/sail artisan migrate:refresh --seed
./vendor/bin/sail artisan test
./vendor/bin/sail artisan key:generate
./vendor/bin/sail npm install --save-dev newman
./vendor/bin/sail npm install
./vendor/bin/sail npm run dev


